  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Description</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summoner Rise is a topdown role-playing game in which players take on the role of a character who is sucked into another world by a computer and embarks on their way home </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players have multiple skills and dozens of different equipment, and the special entries of the equipment will directly affect the effect of the skills, and even change the original skill form to become more powerful</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/4ce5c95b56121cb100fbcf36991ad971.avif?t=1773649778\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras_big/4ce5c95b56121cb100fbcf36991ad971.webp?t=1773649778 width=1560 height=795 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spells of Diversity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/0033ccc94fed368cb638f1403cd26a35.avif?t=1773649778\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras_big/0033ccc94fed368cb638f1403cd26a35.webp?t=1773649778 width=1560 height=795 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore treasure chests and unexpected surprises</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/924727a61c737d854e891e9c5fdb4a9a.avif?t=1773649778\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras_big/924727a61c737d854e891e9c5fdb4a9a.webp?t=1773649778 width=1560 height=846 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Powerful boss battles, tense and exciting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras/311e32f970ef927939d19e57b83074d6.avif?t=1773649778\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030010/extras_big/311e32f970ef927939d19e57b83074d6.webp?t=1773649778 width=1560 height=782 /></span></p>",
